  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nSync through skipped slot of 266176 and stop and then I cannot restart the chain, it gets stuck after fetching the 1st round in initial sync because blocks are not processed\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nWe can start the chain from a skipped slot\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n+ Sync through skipped slot 266176 (or any skipped slot that can be come finalized checkpoint)\r\n+ ArchiveTask found it as finalized checkpoint and store respective state\r\n+ stop beacon node\r\n+ Restart again, fetch slot 266177\r\n+ Try to find preState of parent of 266177 which is 266175 but not found state for it, throw error at https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/master/packages/lodestar/src/chain/blocks/stateTransition.ts#L38\r\n\r\n",
